# Architecture Overview (v2.1)

**Agent rules:** `doc/ARCHITECTURE_V2_AGENT_RULES.md` · **Full guide:** `doc/ARCHITECTURE.md`

Monorepo: React/Vite at root, Express/PostgreSQL in `backend/`, Electron in `electron/`, shared packages in `shared/`.

**Single source of truth:** PostgreSQL.

## Runtime Architecture

**Desktop Edition**

```
Electron → React → apiClient (/api/v1) → Express API → modules (routes→services→repositories) → FinancialPostingService → PostgreSQL
```

**Cloud Edition**

```
Browser → React → apiClient (/api/v1) → Express API → modules (routes→services→repositories) → FinancialPostingService → PostgreSQL
```

Shared calculation logic: `shared/financial-core/`, `shared/report-engines/`.

## Editions & Environments

| Edition | Client | API port | Database |
|---------|--------|----------|----------|
| Desktop (production) | Electron | 3000 | `pbookspro` |
| Desktop (staging) | Electron | 3001 | `pBookspro_Staging` |
| Cloud | Browser | 3000 / 3001 | PostgreSQL |
| API server | — | 3000 / 3001 | PostgreSQL |

> **Deprecated:** Offline SQLite (`VITE_LOCAL_ONLY`, `sqliteBridge`, `services/database/`). Do not extend.

## Strangler: New Code Uses v2.1

Legacy `backend/src/routes/` + flat `services/` are thin delegates only. **Client SQLite removed (Phase 6).** New features go in `backend/src/modules/<domain>/` with `TenantRepository` subclasses.

**Progress:** `doc/ARCHITECTURE_V2_1_MODERNIZATION_PROGRESS.md`

## Where to Put New Code

| Concern | Location |
|---------|----------|
| Domain API | `backend/src/modules/<domain>/` (routes, services, repositories) |
| GL writes | `FinancialPostingService` only |
| Migrations | `database/migrations/NNN_name.sql` (PostgreSQL only) |
| Financial/report logic | `shared/financial-core/`, `shared/report-engines/` |
| API client | `services/api/` (base `/api/v1`) |
| UI | `components/<domain>/` or `modules/<feature>/` |

## Reference Features

- Dashboard snapshots: `modules/dashboard/` → `GET /dashboard/snapshots`
- Financial posting: `FinancialPostingService` → `JournalRepository`
- Custom reports: `modules/reporting/`

## Anti-Patterns

- SQL in routes; direct GL writes outside FinancialPostingService
- Missing tenant_id; editing AUTO-GENERATED backend/financial files
- New calculation logic in components/ (use shared/report-engines/)
- Broad useAppContext() in new code; new handlers in legacy flat routes
- SQLite code or schemas for new development

